                    <span>This book covers a wide range of ethernet issues including fiber optics, 1000BASE-X, hubs, switches and trouble Shooting. This is an excellent reference. The glossary was better than average. Ethernet the Definitve Guide covers everything most people will ever want to know ethernet networking.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The definitive guide - without a doubt</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
